description: This file defines a complex setup of AI agents, tools, and teams for a multi-purpose AI system, including web search, finance data retrieval, image analysis, audio analysis, code execution, and reasoning. It initializes various agents with specific roles, models, tools, and instructions, and then demonstrates their usage through sample responses.

classes.name: Agent
classes.description: Represents an AI agent with specific roles, models, tools, and instructions.

classes.name: Team
classes.description: Represents a team of agents with coordinated instructions and modes.

methods.description: Method used to generate and output responses from the agent team.
